&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="sonuc-ve-cagri-hangisini-kullanacagini-biliyor-musun"&gt;Sonu&amp;ccedil; ve &amp;Ccedil;a&amp;gbreve;r&amp;inodot;: Hangisini Kullanaca&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; Biliyor musun?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Art&amp;inodot;k &lt;code&gt;.xinitrc&lt;/code&gt; ile &lt;code&gt;.xprofile&lt;/code&gt; aras&amp;inodot;ndaki farklar&amp;inodot; biliyorsun. Display Manager kullan&amp;inodot;yorsan, t&amp;uuml;m ba&amp;scedil;lang&amp;inodot;&amp;ccedil; komutlar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;.xprofile&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; dosyana ta&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;.
Bu sayede ba&amp;scedil;lat&amp;inodot;lamayan servisler, &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;mayan tema ayarlar&amp;inodot;, eksik ikonlar gibi dertlerden kurtul!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üëá
&lt;strong&gt;Sen de &lt;code&gt;.xinitrc&lt;/code&gt; mi yoksa &lt;code&gt;.xprofile&lt;/code&gt; mi kullan&amp;inodot;yorsun? Deneyimlerini yorum olarak payla&amp;scedil;!&lt;/strong&gt;
Sorular&amp;inodot;n varsa da &amp;ccedil;ekinmeden yaz! üí¨&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="Masa√ºst√º Ortamlarƒ±"/><category term="lightdm"/><category term="xinitrc"/><category term="xprofile"/><category term="arch linux"/><category term="oturum ayarlarƒ±"/></entry><entry><title>i3lock ile Uyku Modundan Uyanƒ±rken Otomatik Kilit Ekranƒ± Nasƒ±l Ayarlanƒ±r?</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/i3lock-uyku-modu-kilit-ekrani/" rel="alternate"/><published>2025-04-24T14:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.github.io,2025-04-24:/i3lock-uyku-modu-kilit-ekrani/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;i3lock kullanarak Linux sisteminiz uyku modundan uyandƒ±ƒüƒ±nda ekranƒ±n otomatik olarak kilitlenmesini saƒülayƒ±n. Bu rehber, systemd servisleriyle nasƒ±l yapƒ±landƒ±rƒ±lacaƒüƒ±nƒ± adƒ±m adƒ±m g√∂steriyor.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h1 id="i3lock-ile-uyku-modundan-uyanirken-otomatik-kilit-ekrani-nasil-ayarlanir"&gt;i3lock ile Uyku Modundan Uyan&amp;inodot;rken Otomatik Kilit Ekran&amp;inodot; Nas&amp;inodot;l Ayarlan&amp;inodot;r?&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Linux kullan&amp;inodot;yorsan&amp;inodot;z ve bilgisayar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z uyku modundan uyand&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;nda otomatik olarak ekran&amp;inodot;n kilitlenmesini istiyorsan&amp;inodot;z, do&amp;gbreve;ru yerdesiniz. Bu rehberde, pop&amp;uuml;ler ekran kilitleyici &lt;strong&gt;i3lock&lt;/strong&gt; (&amp;ouml;zellikle &lt;code&gt;i3lock-color&lt;/code&gt;) ile bu i&amp;scedil;lemi nas&amp;inodot;l yapabilece&amp;gbreve;inizi anlataca&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;m.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;G&amp;uuml;venlik &amp;ouml;nemli, &amp;ouml;zellikle bilgisayar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; k&amp;inodot;sa s&amp;uuml;reli&amp;gbreve;ine bile olsa ba&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;bo&amp;scedil; b&amp;inodot;rak&amp;inodot;yorsan&amp;inodot;z. &amp;Idot;&amp;scedil;te &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;z&amp;uuml;m: &lt;code&gt;systemd&lt;/code&gt; ile entegre &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;an otomatik bir ekran kilit sistemi. üëá&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="hazirlik-gereksiz-ekran-kilitleyicileri-devre-disi-birakin"&gt;üì¶ Haz&amp;inodot;rl&amp;inodot;k: Gereksiz Ekran Kilitleyicileri Devre D&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot; B&amp;inodot;rak&amp;inodot;n&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;Idot;lk ad&amp;inodot;m, sisteminizdeki mevcut ekran kilitleyicilerin otomatik devreye girmesini engellemek. Ben &lt;strong&gt;KDE&lt;/strong&gt; masa&amp;uuml;st&amp;uuml; ortam&amp;inodot; kullan&amp;inodot;yorum (Arch Linux &amp;uuml;zerinde), bu y&amp;uuml;zden &lt;strong&gt;KScreenLocker&lt;/strong&gt; ayarlar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; &amp;scedil;u &amp;scedil;ekilde d&amp;uuml;zenledim:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="RKScreenLocker ayarlar&amp;inodot;" class="responsive-img" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, (max-width: 992px) 80vw, (max-width: 1400px) 70vw, 60vw" src="/images/wake-up-lock-xl.webp" srcset="/images/wake-up-lock-sm.webp 300w, /images/wake-up-lock-md.webp 500w, /images/wake-up-lock-xl.webp 800w, /images/wake-up-lock-xl.webp 1200w"/&gt;
‚ö†Ô∏è &lt;em&gt;"Otomatik olarak kilitle" ve "devam etti&amp;gbreve;inde kilitle" gibi se&amp;ccedil;eneklerin i&amp;scedil;aretli olmad&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;ndan emin olun.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ard&amp;inodot;ndan &lt;code&gt;i3lock&lt;/code&gt;'un sisteminizde kurulu oldu&amp;gbreve;undan emin olun. Tavsiyem: &lt;a href="https://github.com/Raymo111/i3lock-color" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;i3lock-color&lt;/a&gt;'u tercih etmeniz. Daha fazla &amp;ouml;zelle&amp;scedil;tirme se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;i sunuyor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="arch-tabanlilar-icin_1"&gt;Arch tabanl&amp;inodot;lar i&amp;ccedil;in&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;yay&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;i3lock-color&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;# Arch tabanl&amp;inodot;lar i&amp;ccedil;in&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h1 id="debian-tabanlilar-icin"&gt;Debian tabanl&amp;inodot;lar i&amp;ccedil;in&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;apt&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;install&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;autoconf&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;gcc&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;make&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;pkg-config&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libpam0g-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libcairo2-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libfontconfig1-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxcb-composite0-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libev-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libx11-xcb-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxcb-xkb-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxcb-xinerama0-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxcb-randr0-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxcb-image0-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxcb-util0-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxcb-xrm-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxkbcommon-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libxkbcommon-x11-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libjpeg-dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libgif-dev
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
