&lt;h2 id="adim-1-kilit-komut-dosyasini-olusturun"&gt;üîê Ad&amp;inodot;m 1: Kilit Komut Dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; Olu&amp;scedil;turun&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;Idot;lk olarak, ekran kilitleme komutlar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; i&amp;ccedil;eren bir bash script olu&amp;scedil;tural&amp;inodot;m:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;mkdir&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-p&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;~/scripts
nano&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;~/scripts/i3lock.sh
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;Idot;&amp;ccedil;eri&amp;gbreve;i &amp;scedil;&amp;ouml;yle olacak:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="ch"&gt;#!/bin/bash&lt;/span&gt;
i3lock&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;# Kullanmak istedi&amp;gbreve;iniz parametrelerle birlikte. i3lock -h ile se&amp;ccedil;enekleri g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nt&amp;uuml;leyebilirsiniz.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dosyay&amp;inodot; kaydedin ve &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;labilir yap&amp;inodot;n:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;chmod&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;+x&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;~/scripts/i3lock.sh
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="adim-2-systemd-servisini-tanimlayin"&gt;‚öôÔ∏è Ad&amp;inodot;m 2: systemd Servisini Tan&amp;inodot;mlay&amp;inodot;n&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;Scedil;imdi, uyku modundan &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;k&amp;inodot;ld&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;nda yukar&amp;inodot;daki script&amp;rsquo;in otomatik &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;mas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; sa&amp;gbreve;layacak bir &lt;code&gt;systemd&lt;/code&gt; servisi olu&amp;scedil;turaca&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;z.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;nano&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;/etc/systemd/system/wakelock@.service
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ve a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki i&amp;ccedil;eri&amp;gbreve;i yap&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;n:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;INI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;[Unit]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="na"&gt;Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;Uyku modundan &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;k&amp;inodot;nca ekran&amp;inodot; kilitle&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="na"&gt;Before&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;sleep.target suspend.target&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="k"&gt;[Service]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="na"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;%i&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="na"&gt;Type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;forking&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="na"&gt;Environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;DISPLAY=:0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="na"&gt;ExecStart&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;/home/%i/scripts/i3lock.sh&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="k"&gt;[Install]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="na"&gt;WantedBy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;sleep.target suspend.target&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rma, &lt;code&gt;DISPLAY=:0&lt;/code&gt; tan&amp;inodot;m&amp;inodot; sayesinde X oturumunu tan&amp;inodot;mlar ve belirtilen kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot; i&amp;ccedil;in script&amp;rsquo;i &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;r.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="adim-3-servisi-etkinlestirin"&gt;üöÄ Ad&amp;inodot;m 3: Servisi Etkinle&amp;scedil;tirin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Servisi etkinle&amp;scedil;tirip an&amp;inodot;nda ba&amp;scedil;latmak i&amp;ccedil;in a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutu kullan&amp;inodot;n:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;systemctl&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;enable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;wakelock@&amp;lt;KULLANICI_ADINIZ&amp;gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;--now
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yerine kendi kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot; ad&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; yazmay&amp;inodot; unutmay&amp;inodot;n. &amp;Ouml;rnek:
&lt;code&gt;sudo systemctl enable wakelock@yucel --now&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bundan sonra, sisteminiz her uyku modundan d&amp;ouml;nd&amp;uuml;&amp;gbreve;&amp;uuml;nde otomatik olarak &lt;code&gt;i3lock&lt;/code&gt; ekran kilitleyicisi devreye girecek. üîí&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="yapilandirma-guncellemeleri-nasil-uygulanir"&gt;üîÅ Yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rma G&amp;uuml;ncellemeleri Nas&amp;inodot;l Uygulan&amp;inodot;r?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Script&amp;rsquo;te ya da servis dosyas&amp;inodot;nda bir de&amp;gbreve;i&amp;scedil;iklik yapt&amp;inodot;ysan&amp;inodot;z, t&amp;uuml;m sistemi yeniden ba&amp;scedil;latman&amp;inodot;za gerek yok. A&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutla servisi yeniden ba&amp;scedil;latman&amp;inodot;z yeterli:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;systemctl&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;restart&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;wakelock@&amp;lt;KULLANICI_ADINIZ&amp;gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="sonuc"&gt;üìù Sonu&amp;ccedil;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu yaz&amp;inodot;da, i3lock ve systemd kullanarak Linux sisteminizi daha g&amp;uuml;venli hale getirmenin pratik bir yolunu &amp;ouml;&amp;gbreve;rendiniz. Minimal ama etkili bir yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rma ile, bilgisayar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z uyku modundan uyand&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;nda ekran&amp;inodot;n otomatik olarak kilitlenmesini sa&amp;gbreve;layabilirsiniz. Bu t&amp;uuml;r g&amp;uuml;venlik &amp;ouml;nlemleri, &amp;ouml;zellikle ta&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;nabilir cihazlarda b&amp;uuml;y&amp;uuml;k &amp;ouml;nem ta&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;yor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üí¨ E&amp;gbreve;er bu rehber i&amp;scedil;inize yarad&amp;inodot;ysa, yorum b&amp;inodot;rakarak bana destek olabilirsiniz. Sorular&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z ya da &amp;ouml;nerileriniz varsa duymaktan memnuniyet duyar&amp;inodot;m!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;</content><category term="Masa√ºst√º Ortamlarƒ±"/><category term="i3lock"/><category term="systemd"/><category term="linux g√ºvenlik"/><category term="ekran kilidi"/><category term="suspend"/></entry><entry><title>Linux Tema Nasƒ±l Y√ºklenir (Gnome Shell ve Eklentileri)</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/linux-tema-nasil-yuklenir/" rel="alternate"/><published>2018-09-21T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.github.io,2018-09-21:/linux-tema-nasil-yuklenir/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Linux'ta tema y√ºkleme i≈ülemi olduk√ßa basittir. Gnome Shell ve eklentileri kullanarak nasƒ±l √∂zelle≈ütirme yapabileceƒüinizi bu rehberde adƒ±m adƒ±m anlatƒ±yoruz.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Merhaba, uzun s&amp;uuml;redir bloga bir &amp;scedil;eyler yazm&amp;inodot;yordum. Daha &amp;ouml;nce Unity kullan&amp;inodot;rken video &amp;ccedil;ekmi&amp;scedil;tim, ancak sabit diskimin bozulmas&amp;inodot; ve s&amp;inodot;cak hava derken g&amp;uuml;nler h&amp;inodot;zla ge&amp;ccedil;ti. üòÉ Linux'ta tema y&amp;uuml;kleme i&amp;scedil;lemi olduk&amp;ccedil;a kolayd&amp;inodot;r. Hangi da&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;t&amp;inodot;m&amp;inodot; veya masa&amp;uuml;st&amp;uuml; ortam&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; kullan&amp;inodot;yor olursan&amp;inodot;z olun, s&amp;uuml;re&amp;ccedil; genellikle benzerdir. &amp;Ouml;rne&amp;gbreve;in, Unity i&amp;ccedil;in &lt;code&gt;unity-tweak-tool&lt;/code&gt; kullan&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;rken, Gnome i&amp;ccedil;in &lt;code&gt;gnome-tweak-tool&lt;/code&gt; tercih edilmektedir. XFCE kulland&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;m d&amp;ouml;nemde, &amp;ouml;zelle&amp;scedil;tirmeleri do&amp;gbreve;rudan yapabiliyorduk (yan&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;yor olabilirim ü§î).&lt;/p&gt;
